@node The Perfect Setup
@section The Perfect Setup

The Perfect Setup for using Dezyne is to use the Dezyne IDE,
@pxref{Top, ,,dezyne-ide,the Dezyne IDE Manual}.

The Perfect Setup to hack on Dezyne is basically the perfect setup used
for GNU Guile hacking (@pxref{Using Guile in Emacs,,, guile, GNU Guile
Reference Manual}).  To work on real-life Dezyne projects, you need more
than an editor: you need an IDE, @pxref{Top, ,,dezyne-ide,the Dezyne IDE
Manual}.

@table @code
@item GNU Emacs
To edit @file{.DZN} files, use @file{emacs/dzn-mode.el}.
